<span style="font-weight: 400;">According to her, the main cause of Crohn's disease is: </span><b>Fear. Worry. Not feeling good enough.</b>

<span style="font-weight: 400;">One of the ways of healing this is through saying or writing affirmations.¬†</span>

<span style="font-weight: 400;">Her affirmation for healing Crohn's disease is: </span><b>I digest and assimilate all new experiences peacefully and joyously. I am enough.</b>";s:6:"parent";s:1:"0";s:5:"count";s:1:"0";}}